    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed consistent with MRL 2 scope. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts NIH within 12% and ΔP within 4% of experimental measurements across the full COU operating envelope. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at the identified worst-case operating condition (6.0 L/min, 3500 RPM). The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the COU decision for this Class II CPB device.",
